Perhaps unsurprisingly, Justin Bieber was named as the celebrity holiday partner from hell. 

His recent restaurant bust-up with Orlando Bloom in Ibiza and brushes with the law earned 37 per cent of the vote for worst travel partner.

Katie Price (15 per cent), Piers Morgan and Nick Clegg (12 per cent each), and Miley Cyrus (eight per cent) feature on the unflattering list.

