Suniel Makh, Brand Director at Icelolly, said: 'Celebrities obviously lead a very lavish lifestyle which we all dream of emulating whilst on holiday – attempting to escape reality in the pursuit of relaxation and that all-important star treatment.

'However, it seems money isn't always everything and Brits still very much value the experience and memories that a decent travel partner can provide. 

'And let's face it…a break away with Bieber could very well result in trouble and unnecessary stress!'

